            <p>Hinduism has a vast pantheon of gods and goddesses. Some of the major deities include Brahma (the creator), Vishnu (the preserver), Shiva (the destroyer), Lakshmi (goddess of wealth), and Saraswati (goddess of knowledge).</p>
